{"id":1199,"date":"2021-02-16T21:51:24","date_gmt":"2021-02-16T16:21:24","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost?page_id=1199"},"modified":"2023-11-06T23:20:56","modified_gmt":"2023-11-06T17:50:56","slug":"il","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/localhost\/?page_id=1199","title":{"rendered":"Illustration &#8211; Logo, Mandal, Typeface"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-100 has-custom-font-size is-style-outline has-small-font-size\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-foreground-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/\" style=\"border-radius:100px;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">Homepage<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-100 has-custom-font-size is-style-outline has-small-font-size\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/?page_id=2873\/\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgb(1,1,1) 0%,rgb(97,0,0) 52%,rgb(0,0,0) 100%);padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">Miscellaneous Random<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Here are some illustrations done using AutoCAD, Font Lab and Illustrator. Here all are downscaled to less than 1000-pixel height and width.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"645\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/Picture19.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2898\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/Picture19.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/Picture19-300x194.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/Picture19-150x97.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/Picture19-768x495.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/Picture19-500x323.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/Picture19-800x516.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">This is a font I created, by first drafting it in AutoCAD, exporting it to Illustrators to correct the lines and adjust the spaces, then exported each letter into Font Lab, making the kerning right. I call it &#8220;Cirline&#8221;, and yeah, it&#8217;s not for regular use, it&#8217;s too abstract. This font can be installed in the PC, I can provide the file.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"797\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/bgbgbg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2891\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/bgbgbg.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/bgbgbg-300x239.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/bgbgbg-150x120.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/bgbgbg-768x612.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/bgbgbg-500x399.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/bgbgbg-800x638.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">The distorted background of the homepage, it&#8217;s a collage of my artworks.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"773\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/chain.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2892\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/chain.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/chain-300x232.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/chain-150x116.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/chain-768x594.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/chain-500x387.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/chain-800x618.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">A logo.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"951\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/dodge.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2893\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/dodge.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/dodge-300x285.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/dodge-150x143.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/dodge-768x730.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/dodge-500x476.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/dodge-800x761.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Another logo, bad taste.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"904\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/mandal.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2895\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/mandal.jpg